19
00:02:55,220 --> 00:02:57,340
What is stand-up comedy?

20
00:02:58,850 --> 00:03:00,780
Wu performs stand-up comedy?

21
00:03:02,500 --> 00:03:03,500
I don't know.

22
00:03:04,500 --> 00:03:06,730
She's so talented.
How could you not know?

23
00:03:08,340 --> 00:03:10,130
Chairman, I really don't know.

24
00:03:12,130 --> 00:03:13,890
Do I have any plans
for tomorrow night?

25
00:03:14,890 --> 00:03:15,730
Not at the moment.

26
00:03:15,730 --> 00:03:17,340
Then get us the tickets.

27
00:03:17,500 --> 00:03:18,890
I want to go watch it.

28
00:03:19,410 --> 00:03:20,610
Zheng Hao can come with me.

29
00:03:21,340 --> 00:03:22,180
Okay.

30
00:03:23,780 --> 00:03:24,620
Alright.

31
00:03:24,640 --> 00:03:26,340
Dear audience,

32
00:03:26,540 --> 00:03:28,340
welcome to Sitan Mansion.

33
