The performance is about to begin.

34
00:03:30,450 --> 00:03:31,690
Please set your mobile phones

35
00:03:31,690 --> 00:03:34,380
to silent mode or turn it off.

36
00:03:34,610 --> 00:03:37,130
During the performance,
please do not take photos,

37
00:03:37,220 --> 00:03:38,780
videos or audio recordings.

38
