701
00:34:26,690 --> 00:34:27,690
You like him too?

702
00:34:27,690 --> 00:34:28,690
Of course.

703
00:34:28,690 --> 00:34:31,570
He is an outstanding representative
of Chinese stand-up comedy.

704
00:34:31,610 --> 00:34:32,690
A towering figure.

705
00:34:34,170 --> 00:34:35,420
I don't think so.

706
00:34:36,420 --> 00:34:37,260
Maybe

707
00:34:37,460 --> 00:34:38,900
