741
00:35:58,820 --> 00:36:01,210
The employees of your company

742
00:36:01,210 --> 00:36:03,090
are truly talented.

743
00:36:03,940 --> 00:36:06,210
I'm also impressed.

744
00:36:06,570 --> 00:36:07,410
Right?

745
00:36:09,090 --> 00:36:11,820
Do you dare
to joke about the Chairman?

746
00:36:12,940 --> 00:36:14,300
She's done that already.

747
00:36:15,130 --> 00:36:16,130
Sitan Mansion,

748
00:36:16,170 --> 00:36:17,980
in front of many people,

749
00:36:18,170 --> 00:36:19,690
making fun of me.

750
00:36:21,050 --> 00:36:22,940
You are really something.

751
00:36:24,300 --> 00:36:25,690
You are even more impressive.

752
00:36:26,130 --> 00:36:28,780
People should
have some hobbies, right?

753
00:36:29,050 --> 00:36:30,170
I don't want my employees

754
00:36:30,170 --> 00:36:32,530
to be workaholics.

755
00:36:32,690 --> 00:36:34,090
That's absolutely right.

756
00:36:34,210 --> 00:36:35,940
I just can't stand
some domestic companies

757
00:36:35,940 --> 00:36:37,260
that focus on performance only.

758
00:36:37,490 --> 00:36:38,780
It's too narrow-minded.

759
00:36:41,740 --> 00:36:43,690
Let's keep today's
conversation private.

760
00:36:43,690 --> 00:36:45,130
Make sure not to tell Mr. Xu.

761
00:36:50,010 --> 00:36:50,850
Come on,

762
00:36:51,090 --> 00:36:54,050
I prepared a welcome dinner for you.

763
00:36:54,130 --> 00:36:55,340
Thank you so much.

764
00:36:56,380 --> 00:36:58,820
Wishing you great success at home.

765
00:37:00,260 --> 00:37:03,570
Wishing us great success.

