00:39:29,130 --> 00:39:31,980
that a person who doesn't have a dream

821
00:39:32,570 --> 00:39:34,690
is no different from a dawdler.

822
00:39:36,460 --> 00:39:39,260
Lately, I studied domestic
stand-up comedy and found

823
00:39:39,460 --> 00:39:41,130
although there are a few clubs,

824
00:39:41,130 --> 00:39:42,570
they are all less known.

825
00:39:42,570 --> 00:39:44,620
Over the past few years,
only a few new ones opened,

826
00:39:44,620 --> 00:39:46,170
yet quite a few old ones
have closed.

827
00:39:46,170 --> 00:39:48,570
It seems this path is a dead end.

828
00:39:49,300 --> 00:39:50,690
Let's be realistic here,

829
00:39:50,740 --> 00:39:52,170
it's simply impossible

830
00:39:52,170 --> 00:39:53,940
for us to treat this
as a professional career

831
00:39:53,940 --> 00:39:55,490
like they do abroad.

832
00:39:55,740 --> 00:39:57,820
We cannot abandon a broad avenue

833
00:39:58,210 --> 00:40:00,490
for a dead-end street.

834
00:40:00,820 --> 00:40:02,690
Lu Xun once said,

835
00:40:02,690 --> 00:40:04,690
there was originally
no road in this world,

836
00:40:04,690 --> 00:40:06,130
but as more people walked on it,

837
00:40:06,290 --> 00:40:07,210
a road was formed.

838
00:40:07,570 --> 00:40:09,090
If no one does stand-up comedy,

839
00:40:09,090 --> 00:40:10,690
it'll never have a bright future.

840
00:40:10,690 --> 00:40:11,860
If everybody thinks like this,

841
00:40:11,860 --> 00:40:13,250
we might as well just sell this bar.

842
00:40:13,610 --> 00:40:14,980
- Don't, Zhiyong.
- I'm done.

843
00:40:15,740 --> 00:40:17,260
Don't, Zhiyong, don't be angry.

844
00:40:17,260 --> 00:40:20,490
I'm just trying to help Xiuya
think of a solution.

845
00:40:21,050 --> 00:40:22,820
But, actually, it all depends

846
00:40:23,340 --> 00:40:25,260
on what Xiuya decides to do.

847
00:40:29,170 --> 00:40:30,490
Xiuya, Xiuya.

848
00:40:30,610 --> 00:40:31,530
Well…

849
00:40:32,690 --> 00:40:33,530
You are

850
00:40:35,010 --> 00:40:36,300
the most talented

851
00:40:37,050 --> 00:40:38,820
female stand-up comedian I've ever seen,

852
00:40:39,690 --> 00:40:41,940
and the only
female performer in Banghe.

853
00:40:41,940 --> 00:40:44,690
I value you highly
and I hope you can stay.

854
00:40:44,690 --> 00:40:47,210
Of course, I can't
promise you anything

855
00:40:47,260 --> 00:40:48,530
like a promotion or a raise.

856
00:40:48,840 --> 00:40:50,690
And I don't want
to make empty promises,

857
00:40:50,910 --> 00:40:52,220
talking about hope and the future.

858
00:40:52,490 --> 00:40:53,460
It's all nonsense.

859
00:40:54,550 --> 00:40:56,820
But I want to tell you
that I'm not running this bar

860
00:40:57,250 --> 00:40:58,690
as a hobby.

861
00:40:58,780 --> 00:41:00,170
I genuinely want

862
00:41:00,170 --> 00:41:01,340
to make this work,

863
00:41:01,340 --> 00:41:03,530
and I believe I can make this happen.

864
00:41:03,530 --> 00:41:06,820
I believe stand-up comedy has a future.

865
00:41:07,820 --> 00:41:11,570
Put me aside, I hope you can

866
00:41:11,820 --> 00:41:13,260
give yourself a chance,

867
00:41:13,740 --> 00:41:15,570
give stand-up comedy a chance.

868
00:41:16,170 --> 00:41:18,090
Please think again.

869
00:41:18,090 --> 00:41:21,090
What if there's a turnaround, right?

870
00:41:21,690 --> 00:41:22,820
(By saying this,)

871
00:41:23,170 --> 00:41:25,570
(rather than convince Xiuya to stay,)

872
00:41:25,740 --> 00:41:27,780
(Zhiyong was actually trying)

873
00:41:27,780 --> 00:41:29,690
(to persuade himself to hold on.)

874
00:41:30,090 --> 00:41:31,960
(At this moment, no one needed)

875
00:41:31,960 --> 00:41:34,280
(that unrealistic spiritual
nourishment more than Zhiyong.)

876
00:41:34,280 --> 00:41:35,170
Zhiyong…

877
00:41:35,690 --> 00:41:36,530
Well,

878
00:41:36,820 --> 00:41:37,690
you are

879
00:41:37,690 --> 00:41:39,690
seeing Xu Yunfeng, right?

880
00:41:39,690 --> 00:41:41,210
He likes stand-up comedy.

881
00:41:41,690 --> 00:41:44,690
I believe he has the ability
to help you continue.

882
00:41:44,860 --> 00:41:45,700
Right?

883
00:41:46,910 --> 00:41:47,820
That's enough, Zhiyong.

884
00:41:50,490 --> 00:41:52,690
Xiuya, what do you think?

885
00:41:52,690 --> 00:41:54,050
Just tell us.

886
00:41:54,690 --> 00:41:57,210
(Zhiyong's words
indeed moved Xiuya,)

887
00:41:57,490 --> 00:41:58,690
(but at this moment,)

888
00:41:58,980 --> 00:42:01,900
(she only wanted
to grasp the future within reach.)

889
00:42:06,170 --> 00:42:08,090
Thank you for your advice.

890
00:42:10,940 --> 00:42:12,690
But I still think
I should focus on work.

891
00:42:30,460 --> 00:42:32,130
Like I said, it's a good thing.

892
00:42:32,690 --> 00:42:35,050
Xiuya, don't feel bad about it.

893
00:42:42,090 --> 00:42:43,090
Right?

894
00:42:43,610 --> 00:42:46,530
Yes, congratulations, Xiuya.

895
00:42:48,210 --> 00:42:50,690
Yes, it's a good thing.

896
00:42:52,740 --> 00:42:54,210
Will you perform today?

897
00:42:58,010 --> 00:42:58,850
I don't think so.

898
00:43:16,760 --> 00:43:17,940
You'll just give up like this?

899
00:43:23,130 --> 00:43:25,090
You didn't say anything earlier.

900
00:43:25,210 --> 00:43:27,170
You shouldn't listen to other people.

901
00:43:29,130 --> 00:43:30,300
You should listen to yourself.

902
00:43:32,050 --> 00:43:33,090
Then why are you…?

903
00:43:37,170 --> 00:43:38,570
I just think it's a pity.

904
00:43:43,090 --> 00:43:44,130
You're not me.

905
00:43:45,940 --> 00:43:47,530
You don't know what I want.

906
00:43:48,940 --> 00:43:50,690
So how could you
make a decision for me?

907
00:43:57,690 --> 00:43:59,780
No one wants to remain
in the dark forever,

908
00:44:01,010 --> 00:44:03,690
guessing whether the road ahead
is filled with stones or rivers,

909
00:44:03,940 --> 00:44:05,690
or something even more terrifying.

910
00:44:07,490 --> 00:44:09,050
That requires a lot of courage,

911
00:44:10,980 --> 00:44:13,130
the kind that demands
all of one's strength

912
00:44:13,130 --> 00:44:15,090
to gamble with an uncertain future.

913
00:44:16,690 --> 00:44:18,300
I don't have that kind of courage,

914
00:44:18,980 --> 00:44:20,210
nor am I a gambler.

915
00:44:23,090 --> 00:44:23,940
I just want

916
00:44:23,940 --> 00:44:26,170
something tangible that I can hold onto.

917
00:44:26,170 --> 00:44:27,210
What's wrong with that?

918
00:44:29,940 --> 00:44:30,780
But,

919
00:44:31,570 --> 00:44:33,170
is that really what you want?

920
00:44:36,170 --> 00:44:37,260
This is my choice.

921
00:44:47,170 --> 00:44:48,820
We all have our own
moments of cowardice.

922
00:44:50,330 --> 00:44:51,920
We may be afraid
to face certain things.

923
00:44:53,690 --> 00:44:54,530
However,

924
00:44:55,130 --> 00:44:57,170
if we continue to live so timidly,

925
00:44:58,490 --> 00:45:00,170
and don't dare to take that first step,

926
00:45:01,260 --> 00:45:03,050
then our life
will no longer be meaningful.

927
00:45:07,090 --> 00:45:08,780
I'm not talking about you.

928
00:45:09,260 --> 00:45:10,240
I'm talking about myself.

929
00:45:14,740 --> 00:45:15,690
Actually, I…

930
00:45:15,780 --> 00:45:16,620
Xiuya,

931
00:45:18,530 --> 00:45:19,370
you are talking?

932
00:45:19,530 --> 00:45:21,980
Well, your Yunfeng is here.

933
00:45:40,340 --> 00:45:41,490
Is the wine ready?

934
00:45:47,490 --> 00:45:48,330
Good.

935
00:45:48,780 --> 00:45:49,620
Let's do it.

936
00:45:51,170 --> 00:45:52,170
Am I late?

937
00:45:52,170 --> 00:45:53,150
You've finished the show?

938
00:45:53,300 --> 00:45:55,210
No, I'm not going on stage today.

939
00:45:55,530 --> 00:45:57,090
Aren't you scheduled for today?

940
00:46:00,210 --> 00:46:02,130
- Here, Mr. Xu.
- Thank you.

941
00:46:02,130 --> 00:46:04,530
Well, Xiuya…

942
00:46:04,530 --> 00:46:05,370
Sit here.

943
00:46:08,690 --> 00:46:09,530
Thanks.

944
00:46:09,740 --> 00:46:12,690
Xiuya has encountered
a challenge in life.

945
00:46:12,690 --> 00:46:14,690
Hope you can talk to her.

946
00:46:15,570 --> 00:46:16,410
What's wrong?

947
00:46:19,130 --> 00:46:21,130
It's not really a challenge.

948
00:46:21,260 --> 00:46:23,690
The Chairman

949
00:46:23,690 --> 00:46:25,690
wants to promote me
to the department head,

950
00:46:25,690 --> 00:46:28,820
but the condition is I can't
do stand-up comedy in public anymore.

951
00:46:30,460 --> 00:46:31,300
That's all right.

952
00:46:31,740 --> 00:46:36,050
But she can't
do stand-up comedy anymore.

953
00:46:36,170 --> 00:46:38,170
You enjoy her performance, right?

954
00:46:38,170 --> 00:46:39,050
If she quits,

955
00:46:39,060 --> 00:46:40,940
you won't be able
to hear her anymore.

956
00:46:42,130 --> 00:46:44,210
I unconditionally support
any decision made by Xiuya.

957
00:46:44,420 --> 00:46:45,310
As for stand-up comedy,

958
00:46:45,690 --> 00:46:47,300
if she wants, she can perform for me.

959
00:46:49,570 --> 00:46:51,690
What if… I mean,

960
00:46:51,690 --> 00:46:53,090
if I choose stand-up comedy?

961
00:46:54,800 --> 00:46:55,830
I've also seen many people

962
00:46:55,980 --> 00:46:58,170
who take personal interests
as their pursuit in life

963
00:46:58,170 --> 00:46:59,260
and career goals.

964
00:46:59,690 --> 00:47:00,530
They're okay.

965
00:47:01,160 --> 00:47:02,240
Either way, you'll be right.

966
00:47:02,460 --> 00:47:04,280
(Xu Yunfeng's unconditional support)

967
00:47:04,690 --> 00:47:05,740
(made Wu Xiuya)

968
00:47:05,740 --> 00:47:07,490
(fall into greater confusion.)

969
00:47:07,690 --> 00:47:09,980
(It was even harder for her
to make a choice now.)

